WEBVTT

15:26.830 --> 15:27.470 line:80%
Changning!

15:27.470 --> 15:28.430 line:80%
It's all my fault.

15:28.430 --> 15:30.190 line:80%
We were building snowmen
at the village entrance.

15:30.190 --> 15:31.190 line:80%
But I got distracted,

15:31.190 --> 15:33.470 line:80%
and in the blink of an eye,
Changning and Bao'er were gone.

15:33.470 --> 15:34.400 line:80%
Bao'er!

15:34.400 --> 15:35.160 line:80%
Don't worry.

15:35.160 --> 15:36.210 line:80%
We will find them.
